alysis of: the early means of exchange (money) like the use of volume measure of barely and weight measure of copper and silver in Sumer; various instruments establishing property rights such as Kuduru border stones, seals and inserted cones in walls; detailed analysis of the communication system and its components; and the description of the modern financial instruments used to include, for example, limited partnerships.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aCapitalismzEgyptxHistory. 0aCapitalismzIraqxHistory. 0aEconomic historyyTo 500. 4aAltassyrischer Staat. 4aInstitutionenökonomik. 4aMesopotamien. 4aWirtschaftsgeschichte.  aEconomic History.  aInstitutional economics.  aMesopotamia.  aOld Assyrian.1 aGreenwood, Naftali, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2024 Part 1z978311133219208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2023 Englishz978311131913108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2023z9783111318189oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831110658540 cprintz978311106510640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311106553340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783111065533423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783111065533/original  a978-3-11-131913-1  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-133219-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2024 Part 1b2024  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CL  a